# 🕒 Timeline Page

A responsive, elegant **timeline component** built with **React**, **TypeScript**, and **Material UI**. Ideal for portfolios, experience pages, project histories, and educational timelines.

![Timeline Screenshot](https://your-image-url-if-any.com)

---

## 🚀 Live Demo

🔗 **Try it out here:**  
👉 [https://ephemeral-fudge-b0ebb1.netlify.app](https://ephemeral-fudge-b0ebb1.netlify.app)

> *(Note: If the link is a placeholder or temporary, consider updating it.)*

---

## 🛠 Tech Stack

| Technology      | Purpose                     |
|-----------------|-----------------------------|
| ⚛️ React        | Frontend framework           |
| 🟦 TypeScript   | Type-safe JavaScript         |
| ⚡ Vite         | Fast dev environment & build |
| 🎨 Material UI  | UI components & styling      |

---

## 📁 Features

- Responsive timeline layout
- Modern design using Material UI
- Easy to extend with dynamic content
- Built with reusability and modularity in mind

---

## 🧱 Getting Started

```bash
git clone https://github.com/Mooddex/timeline-page.git
cd timeline-page
npm install
npm run dev
```

Then visit:

```
http://localhost:5173
```

---

## 📦 Build

To generate a production build:

```bash
npm run build
```

---

## 💡 Use Cases

- Portfolio timeline (jobs, education)
- Product launch history
- Company milestones
- Case studies / event tracking

---

## 📌 Customization

You can easily customize:
- Timeline items (title, date, icon, description)
- Colors and theme (using MUI theme)
- Layout direction (vertical/horizontal with minor tweaks)

